name: Bohemian Mondrian
description:
This portrait was captured in a Samba circle. 
I only realized how precious this picture was when I was editing it, as soon as I looked at the colors it came to my mind "it's Mondrian" in the background.  
Rodas de Samba usually take place at night in bars and pubs in the city.

Curitiba, Brasil.
2019
